FuncDef: The load vendor information command loads a vendor information customization file to customize vendor information. The load vendor information command loads a vendor information customization file to customize vendor information.

ParaDef.Info:
Name of the vendor information customization file.
The value is a string of 5 to 64 case-sensitive characters (including the file name extension).
The file name extension must be .zip.
The file name cannot contain the following special characters: ~? * /\ : ' | < > [ ] ; $ ` !
